title: 816. Impact Rookies from Schedule Release Games
itunes:title: 816. Impact Rookies from Schedule Release Games
description:
Rhett Lewis and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys give impact rookies from each of the NFL games announced ahead of the official schedule release. Then, the pair discuss how the Falcons improved through the draft.

Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
